form
<html>
<body>
<form>
  <input type="radio" id="html" name="fav_language" value="HTML">
  <label for="html">HTML</label><br>
  <input type="radio" id="css" name="fav_language" value="CSS">
  <label for="css">CSS</label><br>
  <input type="radio" id="javascript" name="fav_language" value="JavaScript">
  <label for="javascript">JavaScript</label>
</form> 
</body>
</html>

1. each input/select/textarea field must have a name attribute to be submitted.
2. If the name attribute is omitted, the value of the input field will not be sent at all.
The for attribute of the <label> tag should be equal to the id attribute of the <input> element to bind them together.

value attribute provides initial value for input field
<input type="text" value="hello">	Displays a single-line text input field
<input type="radio">	                         Displays a radio button (for selecting one of many choices)
<input type="checkbox">	                         Displays a checkbox (for selecting zero or more of many choices)
<input type="submit">	                         Displays a submit button (for submitting the form)
<input type="button">	                         Displays a clickable button
<input type="range" id="a" name="a" value="50">  Displays meter type range of value 
<input type="number" id="b" name="b" value="50"> Displays number
<input type="password" id="pwd" name="pwd">
<input type="reset" value="Reset">               resets all values
<input type="date" id="birthday">
<input type="datetime-local">
<input type="email">
<input type="image">
<input type="file">
<input type="hidden">
<input type="search">
<input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="123-45-678" pattern="[0-9]{3}-[0-9]{2}-[0-9]{3}" required>
<input type="time">
<input type="url">

atttributes
<input type="text" value="John" readonly> -> can not change value
<input type="text" value="John" disabled> -> will not be sent through form
<input type="text" size="50">             -> input box size is 50
<input type="text" maxlength="4" size="4">-> can not add size > 4
<input type="date" min="2000-01-02">
<input type="date" max="2000-01-02">
<input type="file" id="files" name="files" multiple> -> multiple files can be added
<input type="text" id="country_code" name="country_code" pattern="[A-Za-z]{3}">                          -> add pattern
<input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="123-45-678" pattern="[0-9]{3}-[0-9]{2}-[0-9]{3}"> -> placeholder gives hint of what type of data is to be stored
<input type="text" id="username" name="username" required> -> mandatory field to be filled
<input type="number" id="points" name="points" step="3">   -> if step="3", legal numbers could be -3, 0, 3, 6
<input type="text" id="fname" name="fname" autofocus>      -> this field will automatically focused

